          .wolf-item.is-caption.is-caption--left(data-speed="-1")
            .wolf-item-inner
                p.figcaption I've actually developed this site twice. After finishing the first round, Pentagram rebranded Success Academy. SA then asked Makeable to redesign the site a second time to reflect the new branding. We took what we learned the first iteration and made huge improvements to the site.
          .wolf-item.is-caption.is-caption--right(data-speed="-1")
            .wolf-item-inner
